    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "the best thing is teacher and student bonding .Teachers are here experienced and well natured.Teachers here explain each and every topic very clearly .Teachers here behave equally with all students",
          "name": "shruti goyal",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Presence of dispensary with a doctor is the best part of the campus .The dispensary opens to all",
          "name": "shruti goyal",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Placement opportunities provided by the college and various types of competition organised by the campus ,provides great opportunities to students in various fields",
          "name": "shruti goyal",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "I liked college infrastructure. College teachers are good.",
          "name": "Anamika",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Teaching style is very good. Faculty is good.",
          "name": "Anamika",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "As a writer, I published my book with the help from college teachers",
          "name": "Kailash",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "association are there like Physics Association, Hindi Sabha etc . They organise quizzes, essays, drawings etc competitions time to time",
          "name": "Kailash",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "The Teaching Staff is good . Teachers come in class on time and also take strict actions against the students who came late.",
          "name": "Dalvinder Singh",
          "course_tag_name": "BBA"
        },
        {
          "text": "The Campus Facilities is good . Availability of drinking water and electricity is  24*7.",
          "name": "Dalvinder Singh",
          "course_tag_name": "BBA"
        },
        {
          "text": "The Campus Is neet and clean .Raging free campus. And Also Js any body is raging a strict action was taken against him/her.",
          "name": "Dalvinder Singh",
          "course_tag_name": "BBA"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "space of the campus is less.It needs more space",
          "name": "shruti goyal",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "College washroom i disliked very much before construction.",
          "name": "Anamika",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Low space in college, only one hall is present.",
          "name": "Anamika",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "No gardens are present, non-ac rooms. There is no ac in any of one class.",
